abstract: LEAD: Lawyers, real-estate agents, notaries public, travel agents and even some driving instructors have put up signs in recent weeks offering to help illegal aliens sort their way through the complexities of the new immigration law.

abstract: WINNING the World Series or a Super Bowl is primarily a triumph for a city, a festival  for a few.
